            <h1 style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Setup</h1>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><br></p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;">This Set up Includes&nbsp;</p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><br></p>
            <ul style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Design the website</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Create &amp; Published the course</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Configure the certification &amp; Gamification</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Set up the payment acquire</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><br></p>
            <h1 style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Business Workflows</h1>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><br></p>
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Flow 1 : Sell your courses online</h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><br></p>
            <ul style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
            <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Create a product with product type as "course"</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Define the course on the course set the enrollment policy</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Visit the online shop and select the course</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Make the payment and enroll in the course</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><br></p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><br></p>
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Flow 2 : Offer a Discount and Coupon code for Free Product on Course</h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><br></p>
            <ul style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Set up the Price list and Promotion Program</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Add the Course to the Cart</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Apply the Coupon Code</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Make the Payment and Get the Free Product</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><br></p>
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Flow 3: Learning with assessments and certifications</h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><br></p>
            <ul style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Create a course and set the assessment/survey or a live session</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Set the question set score for the assessment</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Start the examination and send certification email if passed</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Provide badges</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><br></p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><br></p>
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Flow 4 : Build an Online engaged Community</h2>
            <ul style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                <li><br></li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Configure the forum settings</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Set the karma rights and ranks</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Allow enrolers to ask questions and give answers</li>
                <li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Set goals and define ranks or badges</li>
            </ul>
